This study plans to learn more about a new test to look at liver function, the HepQuant-Shunt (HQ-Shunt).

 The HQ-Shunt is being evaluated for safety and effectiveness as an alternative to Hepatic Venous Pressure Gradient testing in patients with liver disease.

